See **Establishing connections** section [here](https://github.com/mysqljs/mysql#readme)

     while (true) {
      val1_ = random.int((min = 0), (max = 100));
      val2_ = random.int((min = 0), (max = 100));
      val3_ = random.int((min = 0), (max = 100));
