)&#39;
```

If by contrast you&#39;re willing to eat a performance penalty to retain the original ordering, change `results+=( &quot;${BASH_REMATCH[2]}&quot; )` to `results=( &quot;${BASH_REMATCH[2]}&quot; &quot;${results[@]}&quot; )`.

